Difference between Process and Thread
-------------------------------------

Process
-------

* It is heavy weight process

* It means a program under excution

* creation and termination takes more time

* Does not share data with each other

* System calls are involved


Thread
------
* It is a light weight process

* It means segment of a process

* Creation and termination takes less time

* Shares data with each other

* No system calls are involved.
